 posting which I hope you will enjoy and use on your websites. Some of them are built by me while other have credits but are free to use. \r\n\r\nMost of them are CSS based so this is why this resources are listed under CSS &amp;gt;&amp;gt; menus but you will find, I think, 2 of them which are based on mootools and CSS.\r\n\r\nI know I named it &quot;8 web menus you just can\u2019t miss&quot; but I will upload more examples (if needed) and I will also upload examples from visitors (some of them ...not any...based on quality). I\u2019m curious to see what I\u2019ve missed while looking for the examples below.", "imagename": "", "infoid": 19748, "category": "technology_design", "isanchordig": 1, "ischecked": 1, "isdelete": 0, "categoryclass": "technology", "via": null, "real_tags": ["\u83dc\u5355", "menu", "css"]}, {"url": "http://tutorialblog.org/25-code-snippets-for-web-designers-part5/", "title": "&#187; Web\u8bbe\u8ba1\u8005\u4e0d\u53ef\u9519\u8fc7\u768425\u4e2a\u4ee3\u7801\u7247\u6bb5 (\u7b2c\u4e94\u90e8\u5206)", "tags": "css ", "name": "diglog", "posttime": "2007-05-18 19:02:50", "ip": "221.14.253.185", "mark": 3, "note": "\u7cbe\u5f69\u5185\u5bb9,\u4e0d\u5bb9\u9519\u8fc7.\u6b64\u94fe\u63a5\u6536\u5f55\u6700\u8fd1\u7f51\u4e0a\u5173\u4e8eHTML,CSS,JS\u7b49\u4e0eWeb\u8bbe\u8ba1\u76f8\u5173\u7684\u7cbe\u5f69\u6587\u7ae0~~~~~\r\nPart 5 of the code snippets series sees us take a look at more handy pieces of html, css, javascript and other usefull things to a web designer \u2026", "imagename": "eaa535101ee540418e87d1ce7c78761f.jpg", "infoid": 19745, "category": "technology_design", "isanchordig": 1, "ischecked": 1, "isdelete": 0, "categoryclass": "technology", "via": null, "real_tags": ["css"]}, {"url": "http://news.sohu.com/", "title": "\u641c\u72d0\u65b0\u95fb\u65b0\u7248\u9996\u9875\u6b63\u5f0f\u4e0a\u7ebf", "tags": "\u641c\u72d0 ", "name": "yinyin", "posttime": "2007-05-18 18:44:57", "ip": "58.212.139.92", "mark": 5, "note": "\u6b64\u6b21\u6539\u7248\u641c\u72d0\u6